headline: Citi Remains Bullish on United Airlines Holdings (UAL)
summary: United Airlines Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) is one of the most undervalued travel stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On February 3, Citi lifted the price target on United Airlines Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) to $155 from $153 and maintained a Buy rating on the shares. The firm also added an “upside 90-day catalyst watch” on […]
